result.execSummary:
The defendant Rodney G. Enneper was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case.

  • Child Enticement-Sexual Contact, a class D felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.07(1).
  • Child Enticement-Sexual Contact, a class D felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.07(1).
  • Child Enticement-Sexual Contact, a class D felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.07(1).
  • 1st Degree Sexual Assault of Child without Great Bodily Harm, a class B felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.02(1)(b).
  • Repeated Sexual Assault of Same Child (At Least 3 Violations of 1st or 2nd Degree Sexual Assault), a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.025(1)(e).
  • 2nd Degree Sexual Assault of Child, a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.02(2).
  • 2nd Degree Sexual Assault of Child, a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.02(2).
  • 2nd Degree Sexual Assault of Child, a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.02(2).
  • Child Enticement-Sexual Contact, a class D felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.07(1).
  • 2nd Degree Sexual Assault of Child, a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.02(2).
  • 2nd Degree Sexual Assault of Child, a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.02(2).
